-4f4c-ac12-5dfa1b7d57e0?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbq=
Osa8-6m8ExkRNpU ] are loans which are negotiated privately and are not orig=
inated by banks. They can command much higher interest rates and offer larg=
ely uncorrelated risk profiles.
